    <li>The <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/OpenBSD-5.7/man4/lmc.4?query=lmc&amp;sec=4">lmc(4)</a> driver for Lan Media Corporation SSI/T1/DS1/HSSI/DS3 devices has been removed.
    <li>The <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/OpenBSD-5.7/man4/san.4?query=san&amp;sec=4">san(4)</a> driver for Sangoma Technologies AFT T1/E1 devices has been removed.
