a155 1
    <li>Work started on a new process-containment facility called <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/?query=tame&amp;sektion=2&amp;manpath=OpenBSD-5.8">tame(2)</a>.
d161 1
a161 1
    <li>The <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/?query=worm&amp;sektion=6">worm(6)</a>
d163 13
