    <li>The <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi/OpenBSD-current/man4/ugold.4?query=ugold&amp;sec=4">ugold(4)</a> driver now supports TEMPerHUMV1.x temperature and humidity sensors.
    <li>Improved sensor support for the <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi/OpenBSD-current/man4/upd.4?query=upd&amp;sec=4">upd(4)</a> driver for USB Power Devices (UPS).
